==Spanish==

===Etymology===
Latin ''[[iam]] [[magis]]''

===Adverb=== 
'''jamás'''
# [[never]]
#: ''No lo he visto jamás'' "I've never seen it"
# [[ever]]
#: ''El mejor libro jamás escrito'' "The best book ever written"

====Synonyms====
*[[nunca]] (1)

====Derived terms====
'''nunca jamás''' ''or'' '''jamás de los jamases'''
# never ever
'''para siempre jamás'''
# for ever and ever

